short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension restores old slack navigation

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The part of the Slack community is unhappy that Slack does not allow the rollback of the new design. If you are used to the classic Slack Navigation design and want to continue using it, this extension will help you.
